\c 36
\s Ukubusa kukaJehowahazi
\p
\v 1 Abantu belizwe basebethatha uJehowahazi indodana kaJosiya, bambeka waba yinkosi esikhundleni sikayise eJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 23.30-34.\x*.
\v 2 UJehowahazi wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lantathu esiba yinkosi; wasebusa inyanga ezintathu eJerusalema.
\v 3 Inkosi yeGibhithe yasimsusa eseJerusalema, yahlawulisa ilizwe \w amathalenta\w** esiliva alikhulu lethalenta legolide.
\v 4 Inkosi yeGibhithe yasibeka uEliyakhimi umfowabo abe yinkosi phezu kukaJuda leJerusalema, yaguqula ibizo lakhe \add yathi\add* nguJehoyakhimi. UNeko wasethatha uJehowahazi umfowabo wamletha eGibhithe.
\s Ukubusa kukaJehoyakhimi
\p
\v 5 UJehoyakhimi wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lanhlanu esiba yinkosi; wasebusa iminyaka elitshumi lanye eJerusalema. Wenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe\x + 2 Kho. 23.36,37.\x*.
\v 6 Kwenyukela kuye uNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 2 Kho. 24.1. Hab. 1.6.\x*, wambopha ngamaketane ethusi, ukumusa eBhabhiloni\x + 2 Kho. 24.6.\x*.
\v 7 UNebhukadinezari waseletha okwezitsha zendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* eBhabhiloni, wakufaka ethempelini lakhe eBhabhiloni\x + 36.10,18. 2 Kho. 24.13. Ezra 1.7. Dan. 1.1,2. 5.2.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJehoyakhimi, lamanyala akhe awenzayo, lokwatholakala kuye, khangela, kubhaliwe egwalweni lwamakhosi akoIsrayeli loJuda\x + 2 Kho. 24.5,6.\x*. UJehoyakhini indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\s UJehoyakhini uthunjelwa eBhabhiloni
\p
\v 9 UJehoyakhini\x + 2 Kho. 24.8,9.\x* wayeleminyaka eyisificaminwembili esiba yinkosi; wasebusa inyanga ezintathu lensuku ezilitshumi eJerusalema. Wenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 2 Kho. 24. 8.\x*.
\v 10 Lekuthwaseni komnyaka inkosi uNebhukadinezari\x + 2 Kho. 24.10-17.\x* yathuma yamletha eBhabhiloni, kanye lezitsha eziloyisekayo zendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 36.7.\x*; yasibeka uZedekhiya umfowabo abe yinkosi phezu kukaJuda leJerusalema\x + Jer. 37.1.\x*.
\s Ukubusa kukaZedekhiya
\p
\v 11 UZedekhiya wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lanye esiba yinkosi; wasebusa iminyaka elitshumi lanye eJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 24.18,19. Jer. 52.1,2.\x*.
\v 12 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe; kazithobanga phambi kukaJeremiya umprofethi, \add ekhuluma\add* okomlomo weN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Jer. 21.1-7. 27.12-28. 32.1-5. 37.1-10. 38.14-28.\x*.
\v 13 Laye wasevukela inkosi uNebhukadinezari\x + 2 Kho. 24.20.\x* eyayimfungise ngoNkulunkulu\x + Hez. 17.18.\x*, wenza yaba lukhuni intamo yakhe\x + 30.8.\x*, waqinisa inhliziyo yakhe, okokuthi kaphendukelanga eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + Dute. 2.30.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Futhi zonke induna zabapristi labantu banda ekuphambukeni ngeziphambeko njengawo wonke amanyala ezizwe, bayingcolisa indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyayiyingcwelisile eJerusalema\x + 33.23.\x*.
\v 15 IN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise, yasithuma kubo ngesandla sezithunywa zayo\x + 24.19. Neh. 9.30.\x*, ivuka ngovivi ithuma, ngoba yayilesihawu ebantwini bayo lendaweni yayo yokuhlala.
\v 16 Kodwa babezihleka usulu izithunywa zikaNkulunkulu\x + 30.10.\x*, bedelela amazwi akhe\x + Nani 15.31.\x*, beklolodela abaprofethi bakhe\x + Gen. 27.12. Jer. 32.3. 38.6. Mat. 23.34-37.\x*, lwaze lwavuka ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwamelana labantu bayo kakwaze kwaba leselapho\x + Ezra 5.12.\x*.
\v 17 Ngakho yabenyusela inkosi yamaKhaladiya\x + 2 Kho. 25.1. Dute. 28.49. Ezra 9.7.\x* eyabulala amajaha abo ngenkemba endlini yendlu yabo engcwele, ingahawukeli ijaha lentombi, omdala lexhegu\x + Hlab. 78.63. 79.2,3.\x*; yabanikela bonke esandleni sayo\x + Jobe 12.12. 15.10. 29.8. 32.6.\x*.
\v 18 Lazo zonke izitsha zendlu kaNkulunkulu, ezinkulu lezincinyane, lezinto eziligugu zendlu kaJehova, lezinto eziligugu zenkosi lezeziphathamandla zayo, konke lokhu yakuletha eBhabhiloni\x + 36.7,10. 2 Kho. 25.13-15.\x*.
\v 19 Basebetshisa indlu kaNkulunkulu, badiliza umduli weJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 25.9. Hlab. 74.6,7. 79.1.\x*, batshisa zonke izigodlo zayo ngomlilo\x + 2 Kho. 15.25.\x*, batshabalalisa zonke izitsha zayo eziloyisekayo\x + 32.27.\x*.
\v 20 Yasithumbela eBhabhiloni abasele enkembeni\x + 2 Kho. 25.11.\x*; basebesiba zinceku zayo lezabantwana bayo\x + Jer. 27.7.\x* kwaze kwaba yikubusa kombuso wePerisiya\x + 36.22.\x*;
\v 21 ukugcwalisa ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlomo kaJeremiya\x + Jer. 25.9,11,12. 29.10.\x*, ilizwe lize likholise amasabatha alo\x + Levi 26.34,35,43. Dan. 9.2. Jobe 14.6.\x*; lagcina isabatha zonke izinsuku zencithakalo, kwaze kwagcwaliseka iminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + Levi 25.4,5.\x*.
\s Isimemezelo sikaKoresi
\p
\v 22 Kwathi ngomnyaka wokuqala kaKoresi inkosi yePerisiya, ekugcwalisekeni kwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlomo kaJeremiya, iN\nd kosi\nd* yavusa umoya kaKoresi inkosi yePerisiya ukuthi edlulise isimemezelo embusweni wakhe wonke, njalo langombhalo, esithi:
\p
\v 23 Utsho njalo uKoresi inkosi yePerisiya: IN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamazulu, inginikile yonke imibuso yomhlaba; layo ingilayile ukuyakhela indlu eJerusalema ekoJuda. Ngubani ophakathi kwenu kubo bonke abantu bayo? IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe kayibe laye, enyuke\x + Ezra 1.1-3.\x*.